   - Heptagon: 7 distinct vertices
   - Octagon: 8 distinct vertices
   - Kite: 4 vertices with two pairs of adjacent sides that are equal
   - Trapezoid: 4 vertices forming a quadrilateral with at least one pair of parallel sides

