- Coordinates in order: (60,77), (75,55), (6,60), (22,78), (3,96), (93,90), (60,77)
- Unique coordinates: (60,77), (75,55), (6,60), (22,78), (3,96), (93,90) = 6 unique points
- The last point (60,77) matches the first, so it closes the path
- Answer: 6 vertices = Hexagon (C)

