- Path: "M 65.79,46.49 L 45.36,17.10 L 22.85,32.75 L 43.28,62.14 L 65.79,46.49"
  - Count: 4 unique vertices = Quadrilateral
  - Analyze which type: Check if it has one pair of parallel sides (trapezoid), two pairs of equal adjacent sides (kite), or four right angles (rectangle)
