- First segment: M 8.10,55.86 L 1.74,25.57 (only 2 points - ignore this)
- Second segment: M 1.74,25.57 L 12.08,23.40 L 18.44,53.69 L 8.10,55.86 (4 points - this is the main shape)
- Count: 4 vertices = quadrilateral (trapezoid/kite/rectangle)
- If options show "(K) trapezoid", output only: K
