     * Only classify as "rectangle" if it has right angles and opposite sides clearly equal
     * Only classify as "kite" if it has the distinctive symmetric diamond/kite shape
     * **Default assumption for irregular quadrilaterals should be trapezoid (K), not kite (D) or rectangle (H)**

