   - Point 3: (6.90,59.13) from second L (the second M goes to 75.18,56.50 which is already counted)
   - Point 4: (22.09,77.44) from third L (the third M goes to 6.90,59.13 which is already counted)
   - Point 5: (2.73,94.57) from fourth L (the fourth M goes to 22.09,77.44 which is already counted)
   - Point 6: (91.78,91.66) from fifth L (the fifth M goes to 2.73,94.57 which is already counted)
   - The sixth M goes to 91.78,91.66 (already counted) and the final L returns to 59.64,77.72 (already counted)
   - Total: 6 distinct points = hexagon (C)

